                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Sorsby</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">La Paz</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-05-08">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 8, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Government of Bolivia extends through the legation cordial invitation Secretary
                    of State to visit Bolivia during his southern trip. Bolivian minister at
                    Washington also has been instructed.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Sorsby.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
